cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.MM, cs.AI, cs.LG. 

The paper deals with image compositing, which is a computer vision problem, hence cs.CV is the most likely sub-category. The paper also involves generating realistic images, which falls under the category of generative models, making cs.GR and cs.MM likely sub-categories. The use of GANs and STNs also suggests that the paper could be categorized under cs.AI and cs.LG.
